Love this piece at Promenade mrt! There are four at the station and you can see them from different perspectives throughout the station! Our art in transit tours offers our students opportunities to look closely at the art, discuss it with our guides and their peers and make meaning for themselves! They begin to understand how the artists would together with the architects and a variety of companies to create a unique identity for each station. The artists research the area and create works that tell stories of the different communities throughout Singapore! . .
